    "MissionGiver": "Rough & Ready",
    "Title": "Salvage Wrecked Ships on the Drift",
    "TitleKey": "roughready_salvage_M_title_001",
    "Description": "Got word there\u2019s a few ships near ~mission(Location|Address) just floating all by their lonesome. It\u2019s good salvage, but none of our crews have the time right now. We figured to give you first snap at it.\n\nIf you want the coords, we\u2019ll sell them to you for a price. Then you\u2019re free to pick the wreck as clean as you like and sell it all for a tidy profit. Now, you might run into some trouble out there from rival scavs, but I\u2019m sure it won\u2019t be anything you can\u2019t handle.\n\n- Smokey",
    "DescriptionKey": "roughready_salvage_M_desc_001",
    "DisplayDescription": "Got word there\u2019s a few ships near Checkmate at the L4 Lagrange of Pyro II just floating all by their lonesome. It\u2019s good salvage, but none of our crews have the time right now. We figured to give you first snap at it.\n\nIf you want the coords, we\u2019ll sell them to you for a price. Then you\u2019re free to pick the wreck as clean as you like and sell it all for a tidy profit. Now, you might run into some trouble out there from rival scavs, but I\u2019m sure it won\u2019t be anything you can\u2019t handle.\n\n- Smokey",
